Popular Afropop singer Tiwa Savaged has performed her hit track ‘Koroba’ on stage with a male fan. The performance took place during her “Water and Garri” tour in the US. The event which held at “The Promontory”, Chicago, Illinois saw the excited fan standing opposite Tiwa in a duet, singing “Koroba” word-for-word as they thrilled fans.   Politics in Nigeria not for faint hearted – Davido     Kizz Daniel begs God for ‘full option daughter’     Nkechi Blessing’s ex-lover celebrates peace of mind on…   The “Somebody son’s” singer halted for few moments to watch the male fan in utter amazement. Reacting, to the fan’s energetic performance, 42-year-old Mummy Jam Jam captioned the video: “Ayeeeeeeee, he’s lit.”